TO BUILD AND RUN:
1. Ensure Vulkan SDK is installed
2. Compile shaders: glslc shaders/text.vert -o shaders/text.vert.spv && glslc shaders/text.frag -o shaders/text.frag.spv
3. Add DejaVuSansMono.ttf font to assets/ directory
4. Run: cargo run

